WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:02.416
My name is Cassie, and I see ghosts.

00:02.419 --> 00:04.858
Sometimes they send me a message,

00:04.861 --> 00:06.627
and sometimes they just show up.

00:06.629 --> 00:10.465
If you find yourself wanting
a little help from my side,

00:10.467 --> 00:13.534
just give me a holler,
and I'll come running.

00:13.536 --> 00:16.236
We're not a team. I never
want to see you again.

00:16.239 --> 00:17.538
I can't believe I'm saying this,

00:17.540 --> 00:19.054
but maybe reach out to Cassie.

00:19.057 --> 00:20.351
I saw some strange stuff,

00:20.354 --> 00:23.088
and I think it might
be related to your case.

00:23.091 --> 00:24.489
Who's Sally?

00:24.492 --> 00:26.280
My fiancÃ©e. She fell into a coma.

00:26.282 --> 00:28.816
It's like she's here, but she's gone.

00:28.818 --> 00:30.952
I can see if she'll talk to me.

00:30.954 --> 00:32.835
That'd be great.

00:40.230 --> 00:42.597
You're not going in there, are you?

00:47.103 --> 00:49.604
It's just a hospital.

00:49.606 --> 00:51.839
It'll be fine.

00:51.841 --> 00:55.076
Hospitals are always
crammed full of ghosts.

00:55.078 --> 00:57.578
If you need a bodyguard
to keep them off you,

00:57.580 --> 00:59.514
I'm available.

00:59.516 --> 01:01.082
Go away.

01:01.084 --> 01:02.750
Oh, come on, now.

01:02.752 --> 01:04.986
The quicker you agree
to let me help you,

01:04.988 --> 01:06.921
the quicker I'll be out of your hair.

01:08.925 --> 01:10.625
Why would you want to help me?

01:10.627 --> 01:12.593
Because I need to do some good,

01:12.595 --> 01:14.595
or I'll never get out of here.

01:14.597 --> 01:17.798
Now, I admit, I did some bad things

01:17.800 --> 01:21.168
when I was alive, and
for that, I'm truly sorry.

01:21.170 --> 01:24.338
But it stands to reason
if I start putting my chits

01:24.340 --> 01:26.274
in the "doing good" jar,

01:26.276 --> 01:28.042
mm, maybe folks up there

01:28.044 --> 01:31.445
will let me pass through
those heavenly gates.

01:31.447 --> 01:34.448
I help you, you help me.

01:34.450 --> 01:36.517
What do you say?

01:36.519 --> 01:38.452
I say find another sucker.

01:46.396 --> 01:48.796
Think I'll tag along with you anyhow.

01:48.798 --> 01:52.300
A hospital's a dangerous
place for someone sensitive.

01:52.302 --> 01:56.304
All the people who died in
there, all the pain, fear,

01:56.306 --> 01:57.972
that energy... it lingers.

01:57.974 --> 02:00.374
You can see it and feel it.

02:01.644 --> 02:03.477
I can ease you past the rough spots.

02:07.483 --> 02:10.184
It's only rough at first.

02:10.186 --> 02:14.522
Once I get inside, I can
figure out how to block it...

02:14.524 --> 02:16.525
most of it.

