contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:36.913 --> 02:38.679
Get a move on, slowpoke.

02:44.520 --> 02:45.853
Going up?

02:45.855 --> 02:47.855
Yes, alone.

02:53.863 --> 02:57.187
SRS Tech to Pediatric Oncology ward...

02:57.190 --> 02:58.637
- Hey.
- Can I help you?

02:58.640 --> 03:00.067
I'm here to see Sally Bishop.

03:00.069 --> 03:02.203
Detective Asante called ahead about me.

03:02.205 --> 03:04.472
- You must be Cassie.
- Yeah.

03:04.474 --> 03:06.273
Thank you.

03:06.275 --> 03:09.039
Are you friends with Detective Asante?

03:09.042 --> 03:10.877
Something like that.

03:10.880 --> 03:12.880
Well, he seems very devoted.

03:15.151 --> 03:16.945
Let me know if you need anything.

03:16.948 --> 03:20.043
- Thanks.
- Yeah.

04:17.380 --> 04:20.148
I mean, like it was gonna be that easy.

05:07.940 --> 05:10.107
Oh.

05:12.338 --> 05:14.172
Was that you?

05:14.175 --> 05:16.909
Next time, warn a girl.

05:18.541 --> 05:22.176
Hey. Got you a tea.

05:22.178 --> 05:24.712
Guy said it tastes just
like a Yorkshire Gold.

05:26.015 --> 05:27.681
You're not even gonna taste it?

05:27.683 --> 05:30.217
There's no way that American
swill tastes like anything

05:30.219 --> 05:33.420
but weak, lukewarm, sugary piss.

05:33.422 --> 05:35.356
But I appreciate the thought.

05:35.358 --> 05:36.924
Anytime.

05:36.926 --> 05:39.693
Gentlemen, we've got a
body at Woodgate Memorial.

05:39.695 --> 05:41.195
- Patient or visitor?
- Staff.

05:41.197 --> 05:43.437
- Nurse fell from the roof.
- Suicide?

05:43.440 --> 05:45.770
You tell me.

05:45.773 --> 05:47.873
Officer Jansen.

05:47.876 --> 05:49.869
Good morning, detectives.

05:49.872 --> 05:51.071
Morning.

05:51.073 --> 05:53.407
So, what can you tell us?

05:53.409 --> 05:56.043
Uh, the deceased is Grace Morrow, 37.

05:56.045 --> 05:57.411
She's a registered nurse.

05:57.413 --> 05:59.343
Worked at Woodgate the past two years.

05:59.346 --> 06:00.781
She was in the middle of her shift.

06:00.783 --> 06:02.783
Told her friends that she
was taking a cigarette break.

06:02.785 --> 06:05.219
20 minutes later a
custodian heard a scream,

06:05.221 --> 06:06.720
came out here, and found the body.

06:06.722 --> 06:07.890
Anyone see her fall?

06:07.893 --> 06:09.890
We're canvassing, but nothing so far.

06:09.892 --> 06:11.325
Keep at it, and get somebody

06:11.327 --> 06:13.060
to pull security video from the rooftop

06:13.062 --> 06:14.562
and the stairwell, please.

06:14.564 --> 06:16.130
So what do you think, Amy?

06:16.132 --> 06:18.899
Spinal cord injuries
suggest she folded on impact

06:18.901 --> 06:20.273
like a closing book.

06:20.276 --> 06:21.602
She went over backwards.

06:21.604 --> 06:23.237
That's unusual for suicide.

06:23.239 --> 06:25.673
They don't typically scream either.

06:25.675 --> 06:27.741
Check out the bruising here.

06:31.581 --> 06:33.247
Well, those look like fingertips.

06:36.419 --> 06:38.085
This is where she went over.

06:38.087 --> 06:39.253
So, if someone was up here with her,

06:39.255 --> 06:40.921
maybe they asked for a cigarette.

06:40.923 --> 06:42.423
They step up close.

06:42.425 --> 06:43.991
As she's pulling it out of the pack,

06:43.993 --> 06:45.626
they grabbed her legs
and flipped her backwards

06:45.628 --> 06:46.760
over the ledge.

06:46.762 --> 06:48.629
Detectives?

06:48.631 --> 06:49.964
I'm Hal Weaver.

06:49.966 --> 06:51.632
I'm the administrator here at Woodgate.

06:51.635 --> 06:54.268
Please let him through. Thank you.

06:54.271 --> 06:55.638
Mr. Weaver.

06:55.641 --> 06:57.874
I just want to assure
you that the hospital

06:57.877 --> 07:00.273
will support your investigation
in any way that we can.

07:00.276 --> 07:01.775
Thank you. We appreciate that.

07:01.777 --> 07:03.177
We'll need to interview your staff,

07:03.179 --> 07:04.778
especially anyone Grace
considered a friend.

07:04.780 --> 07:06.359
Vanessa Shaw, she's a nurse

07:06.362 --> 07:08.527
at Pediatric Oncology.

07:08.530 --> 07:10.216
I believe she and Grace were roommates.

07:10.219 --> 07:12.152
- How well did you know Grace?
- Not very.

07:12.154 --> 07:14.521
I try to keep a professional
distance with the employees.

07:14.523 --> 07:17.024
Did Grace have any problems
with a staff member?

07:17.026 --> 07:18.959
Anyone that gave her a hard time?

07:18.961 --> 07:20.914
She never filed any complaints.

07:20.917 --> 07:23.481
Look, as far as I know,
Grace got along with everyone.

07:23.484 --> 07:26.033
I'm sure this is just
a terrible accident.

07:26.035 --> 07:27.868
We have to be thorough. You understand.

07:27.870 --> 07:28.898
Of course.

07:28.901 --> 07:30.970
Mr. Weaver, where were
you when Grace fell?

07:30.973 --> 07:33.641
A board meeting...
second-floor conference room.

07:33.643 --> 07:36.710
I heard a commotion, we ran outside,

07:36.713 --> 07:39.481
and that's when I saw it was Grace.

07:39.484 --> 07:41.273
Is there anything else you need?

07:41.276 --> 07:43.484
That's all for now.
Thanks for your time.

07:43.486 --> 07:44.985
Thank you.

07:44.987 --> 07:46.353
Anything?

07:46.355 --> 07:48.689
Security says that the
cameras in the stairwell

07:48.691 --> 07:51.358
and on the roof malfunctioned
sometime this morning.

07:51.360 --> 07:52.993
There's no video.

07:52.995 --> 07:54.453
Well, that's suspicious, isn't it?

07:54.456 --> 07:55.988
Apparently it happens a lot.

07:55.991 --> 07:59.832
The staff uses the roof as a
kind of unofficial clubhouse.

07:59.835 --> 08:01.335
People even come up here to fool around.

08:01.337 --> 08:03.103
And that's when they
knock out the cameras.

08:03.105 --> 08:04.838
Let's talk to Grace's roommate.

08:04.840 --> 08:06.840
Maybe our victim was meeting someone.

08:12.615 --> 08:16.551
Pediatric physician's
assistant, please call 5300.

08:24.648 --> 08:27.461
Any attending technician to
third floor Radiology, please.

08:27.463 --> 08:30.264
Any attending technician
to third floor Radiology.

08:53.289 --> 08:54.621
Hello?

08:56.792 --> 08:58.660
Hello?

09:00.596 --> 09:01.895
Hello?

09:09.572 --> 09:11.972
Who's there?

09:35.698 --> 09:38.832
Hey. Where are you going?

09:45.808 --> 09:48.275
Hey, there.

09:48.277 --> 09:50.778
Do you want me to come with you?

09:55.117 --> 09:57.951
Please don't be like
the kid from "The Ring."

10:06.210 --> 10:08.495
The basement. Of course.

10:27.328 --> 10:28.805
I'm Cassie.

10:30.611 --> 10:32.611
What's your name?

10:32.614 --> 10:34.480
Ethan.

10:34.483 --> 10:36.450
Ethan Grant.

10:36.453 --> 10:38.991
Well, it's nice to meet you, Ethan.

10:38.994 --> 10:42.596
- What are you doing down here?
- I guess I live here now.

10:42.598 --> 10:44.161
All alone?

10:44.164 --> 10:47.768
With a lady, but she doesn't
like me talking to strangers.

10:47.770 --> 10:49.820
Please get me out of here.

10:51.393 --> 10:52.573
Run!

10:58.347 --> 11:01.115
Leave my boy alone!

11:01.118 --> 11:09.086
